I'm just...

10
00:00:26,436 --> 00:00:28,129
a little distracted.

11
00:00:28,160 --> 00:00:29,850
Is everything okay?

12
00:00:29,877 --> 00:00:32,474
Not really.
We need to talk.

13
00:00:32,502 --> 00:00:35,044
Come on. I got lockjaw
and you want to talk?

14
00:00:35,063 --> 00:00:37,498
I want to know where we're
going with this relationship.

15
00:00:37,518 --> 00:00:38,831
Do we have
any kind of future?

16
00:00:38,852 --> 00:00:41,260
