to each other.

22
00:00:51,432 --> 00:00:52,793
You mean like marriage?

23
00:00:52,812 --> 00:00:54,109
Would that be so awful?

24
00:00:54,133 --> 00:00:55,444
Ask my ex-wife.

25
00:00:55,461 --> 00:00:57,914
Her statement in court read
like a Stephen King novel.

26
00:00:57,937 --> 00:01:00,095
Where is this coming
from all of a sudden?

27
00:01:00,131 --> 00:01:02,081
It was something
my gynecologist said.

28
00:01:02,100 --> 00:01:03,979
- Are you all right?
- I'm fine.

29
00:01:03,999 --> 00:01:06,322
