great down here.

30
00:01:06,353 --> 00:01:08,624
Would you like to
have dinner sometime?"

31
00:01:08,866 --> 00:01:12,868
Wow. Wow. That is
wildly inappropriate.

32
00:01:12,887 --> 00:01:15,254
- I mean, as a doctor myself...
- You're a chiropractor.

33
00:01:15,271 --> 00:01:17,057
Nonetheless,
I am a healer.

34
00:01:17,135 --> 00:01:18,620
There's a code!

35
00:01:18,645 --> 00:01:20,056
I mean, you don't
ask someone out

36
00:01:20,070 --> 00:01:22,193
