their feet in the stirrups.

37
00:01:22,207 --> 00:01:24,103
Unless you're drunk
at a rodeo.

38
00:01:24,736 --> 00:01:26,102
Well, he did.

39
00:01:26,115 --> 00:01:28,117
Do you want to go
out with him?

40
00:01:28,133 --> 00:01:30,166
It's not about
going out with him.

41
00:01:30,184 --> 00:01:32,087
But if you and I
don't have a future,

42
00:01:32,106 --> 00:01:33,912
I need to examine
my options.

43
00:01:33,925 --> 00:01:36,896
The way you got examined
by Dr. Busyfingers?

44
00:01:37,895 --> 00:01:41,277
Look, I don't want
to grow old alone.

45
00:01:41,314 --> 00:01:44,360
So, if you're not ready to make
this kind of commitment,

46
00:01:44,416 --> 00:01:45,927
better to know now.

47
00:01:45,953 --> 00:01:48,754
Geez, Lyndsey, you
kinda sprung this on me.

48
00:01:48,791 --> 00:01:51,718
