a big supporter of the arts.

138
00:06:07,417 --> 00:06:10,077
Oh, really?
How fortuitous.

139
00:06:10,237 --> 00:06:11,735
Ooh, "fortuitous."

140
00:06:11,769 --> 00:06:13,617
You are a writer.

141
00:06:13,730 --> 00:06:16,393
