147
00:06:31,863 --> 00:06:33,640
Oh.

148
00:06:34,781 --> 00:06:36,602
Yum.

149
00:06:40,679 --> 00:06:41,878
Hi.

150
00:06:41,910 --> 00:06:43,043
Hi.

151
00:06:43,085 --> 00:06:44,904
