160
00:07:00,058 --> 00:07:02,025
Anything you want to talk about?

161
00:07:02,047 --> 00:07:03,691
Not yet.

162
00:07:03,847 --> 00:07:05,941
Still thinking.
You know...

163
00:07:05,961 --> 00:07:08,220
percolating,
uh, mulling.

164
00:07:08,241 --> 00:07:10,572
All the pertinent "ings."

165
00:07:11,496 --> 00:07:12,584
Ooh!

166
00:07:12,614 --> 00:07:14,681
Cogitating!

167
00:07:14,814 --> 00:07:17,143
Stalling, avoiding, ducking.

168
00:07:17,170 --> 00:07:19,016
Ooh! Procrastinating.

169
00:07:19,049 --> 00:07:21,688
What? No.
That's-that's crazy.

170
00:07:21,709 --> 00:07:23,575
I'm not doing any
of those things.

171
00:07:23,595 --> 00:07:25,343
I mean, why would I do
those things?

172
00:07:25,362 --> 00:07:27,365
So what movie would you
like to see?

173
00:07:27,564 --> 00:07:29,060
I know what you're doing.

174
00:07:29,090 --> 00:07:30,639
This is not gonna go away.

175
00:07:30,660 --> 00:07:31,710
I just don't understand

176
00:07:31,722 --> 00:07:33,552
why we can't keep things
the way they are.

177
00:07:33,566 --> 00:07:35,130
You mean, living day-to-day,

178
00:07:35,160 --> 00:07:37,252
never knowing what kind of
future you have with the person

179
00:07:37,275 --> 00:07:39,609
