with the past three years?

180
00:07:39,634 --> 00:07:42,823
I prefer to think of it
as cherishing each day,

181
00:07:42,849 --> 00:07:45,907
nay each moment,
with the woman I love

182
00:07:45,947 --> 00:07:48,565
