and broke down.

215
00:09:28,896 --> 00:09:31,946
Ah, I should have told you
not to turn on the radio.

216
00:09:33,688 --> 00:09:35,622
So, uh, what's the good news?

217
00:09:35,660 --> 00:09:37,551
This beautiful woman pulls up

218
00:09:37,565 --> 00:09:39,932
